---
import { WAITLIST_URL } from "../content";
---

<section id="join" class="reveal py-24 md:py-32 border-b border-line">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Columbia students</p>
        <h2
          class="display mt-5 text-[clamp(36px,5.4vw,72px)] text-fg max-w-[20ch]"
        >
          Build the software you'll actually put on your resume.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 md:pt-3">
        <p class="text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.6] text-fg/85">
          Real clients. Real code review. Real shipping. You get paired with a
          3–4 person team and an advisor from BCV, OpenAI, or HBS — then ship a
          deployed product in 1–2 months.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.6] text-fg/85">
          Our members have landed roles at companies like Alibaba, in addition
          to the usual suspects.
        </p>

        <a href={WAITLIST_URL} class="btn-primary mt-9">
          Join the Fall 2026 waitlist
          <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
